condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, 4(a) | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall cause Tianshui Municipality to completeremedial works at Xianren Lake Dam. | Due Date :30-Sep-2008

Finance Agreement :PA, Section I, 4(b) | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall cause Tianshui Municipality to furnisha long-term operation, maintenance and emergency preparedness plan for two project dams | Due Date :30-Sep-2008

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 1 | Description :Project Implementing Entity shall enter into a contract, satisfactory to theBank, for technical assistance to PPMO for management of construction and supervision of project activities | Due Date :01-Sep-2008

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 2 | Description :The PIE shall cause each PIU to furnish to the Bank by December 31, 2010, anoperation and maintenance planfor the heritage and tourism facilities located in their site. | Due Date :31-Dec-2010

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 3 | Description :The Project Implementing Entity shall provide training in financial managementto staff in the MPMOs and PIUs in a manner satisfactory to the Bank | Due Date :31-Dec-2008

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 4 (a) and (b) | Description :The PIU of Jiayuguan Municipality will prepare and submit to theJiayuguan Gov for approval a Development Control Plan for JYG Great Wall Scenic Area | Due Date :31-Dec-2010
